column5: Redemtion for my last outing on this body of water. Last time they would jump and spit. This morning, they met, the terminator.                Then my bait was terminated, Good thing I keep my broken spinner baits. Spare blades.LOL    I,ll take this kind of bite every morning Im out.
good morning, wish I remembered my camera  the phone aint much    nice to fish with air support

and that was with my phone, just think if I has a camera with me  lol
